Narcissus -- Narcissus is thirsty here -- Narcissus is thirsty over here.
Samnis(?) how much(??) do you owe, Felicio, (other letters here)

Pitamnus, Marc "51"? (or Pitamnus, freedman of Marcius)
VIvir/Severus, those whom I at Pompeii...  (no verb written)
Of Persius(?) (following the conventions of bronze stamps with names in the genitive)
On the 7th day before the Ides of September, Quintus Postumius asked Aulus Attius, "Can I screw you?"
The girl was charming to Ceius and many (others)
